'''[[Tehran]]''' is one of the most ethnically diverse cities in [[Asia]]. The city of Tehran (not to be confused with the larger, Tehran Metropolitan) had a population of approximately 8,293,140 in 2011 and the Tehran Province has a 12,183,391 population.<ref name="amar.org.ir">{{cite web|url=http://www.amar.org.ir/Portals/2/census-90/shahrestanha-jamiat-90.xlsx |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2013-08-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201839/http://www.amar.org.ir/Portals/2/census-90/shahrestanha-jamiat-90.xlsx |archivedate=2016-03-04 |df= }}</ref>
