==Ethnic groups==
===Persians=== According to a 2010 census conducted by the Sociology Department of [[Tehran University]] in many districts of Tehran across various socio-economic classes in proportion to population sizes of each district and socio-economic class, 63% of [[persian people]] in [[Tehran]] were born in Tehran, 98% know [[Persian language]], 75% identify themselves as ethnic [[Persian people|Persian]], and 13% have some degree of proficiency in a European language<ref>"Chand Darsad Tehranihaa dar Tehran Bedonyaa Amadand" (How many percent of Tehranis were born in Tehran), accessed December, 2010 [http://www.tabnak.ir/fa/news/133668][http://www.aftabnews.ir/vdchimnzw23nzid.tft2.html][http://www.jahannews.com/vdcgw39qzak9tn4.rpra.html]</ref>
