{{Infobox ethnic group |population=22,700<ref name="Egyres"/> |langs=[[Arabic language|Arabic]] ([[Egyptian Arabic]]){{·}}[[Coptic language|Coptic]]{{·}}[[Dutch language|Dutch]] |rels=Predominantly [[Islam]] ([[Sunni Islam|Sunni]]), minority [[Coptic Orthodox Church of Alexandria|Coptic Christianity]] }}
'''Egyptians in the Netherlands''' are residents or citizens of the [[Netherlands]] who are of [[Egyptians|Egyptian]] ancestry. The community is relatively small, numbering 22,700 individuals.<ref name="Egyres">{{cite web|title=Bevolking; generatie, geslacht, leeftijd en herkomstgroepering, 1 januari|url=http://statline.cbs.nl/StatWeb/publication/?DM=SLNL&PA=37325&D1=0&D2=0&D3=0&D4=0&D5=a&D6=l&VW=T|publisher=Centraal Bureau voor de Statistiek|accessdate=22 April 2016}}</ref>
